Title_Description:
[Run] Fully e2e support different shells process calls From #7292, @davidegiacometti did a great job doing an intial implementation.  On Code review, we saw there are other spots that need improvement, namely context menu

This is a nice fix! In order to fully fix the issue #4622 we should also update both:
Microsoft.Indexer.Plugin\ContextMenuLoader.cs and
Microsoft.Folder.Plugin\ContextMenuLoader.cs

Doing a quick search for `process.Start`, you can see we have other spots that need tweaking

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1462282/96177289-7d266c80-0ee2-11eb-91ef-345fcf8d4ef6.png)

This should be refactored into something a bit more common so pattern can be reused in another spots that do the same shell based start.

`using (var process = new Process())
{
    var directory = Path.GetDirectoryName(record.FullPath);
    process.StartInfo.FileName = directory;
    process.StartInfo.UseShellExecute = true;
     process.Start();
}`

Image Resizer color bit dark on light theme On 0.27, the theme on the top feels off, it is a light grey versus a solid white.

